		<div><br /> I have a single test of SCM3 - from the cleric board - <a href="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/Forum1/HTML/007749.html" target="_blank">eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb...07749.html</a><br />
<br />
Smegal could cast 5 GCH + 1 CH (5900 mana) in estimated 14 ticks of 41 mana/tick - and a mana pool of 4405 if we assume C3 is 250 mana. (255wis, +1305 in mana items)<br />
<br />
Result: 5900 mana worth cast with 4979 mana. Cost reduction = 15.6% or equivalently a gain of 18.5%. <br /></div>
